lFSIA0Bw ...and again in 1989, when Ronnie McDowell took it\u2026", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Meeting Across the River&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Meeting Across the River", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/meeting-across-the-river/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/rosanne_cash_feat_bruce_springsteen-sea_of_heartbreak_s.jpg?fit=450%2C450&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200}, "classes": []}, {"id": 24471, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/01/27/roll-of-the-dice-the-war-song/", "url_meta": {"origin": 68572, "position": 5}, "title": "Roll of the Dice: The War Song", "author": "Ken", "date": "January 27, 2021", "format": false, "excerpt": "Nineteen-year-old Bruce Springsteen grappled with the horrors of the Vietnam War in one of his earliest compositions.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Roll of the Dice&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Roll of the Dice", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/roll-of-the-dice/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/warsong.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/warsong.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/warsong.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/warsong.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/warsong.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}], "_links": {"self": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/68572", "targetHints": {"allow": ["GET"]}}], "collection": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}], "about": [{"href": "htt